{
  "stem": "2713.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He took us in, and while we were there, we begged the gentleman if he could do something about our parents because we were worrying very much.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he said, look, tomorrow morning I'm going to the city, to Jaworszice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if they agree to come, I would bring them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were so happy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when he came back, [SOBBING] we knew that they're not alive anymore, because when you looked at his face, you could read, and you could-- you could see that something has happened.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he told us the bad news, that our parents were killed there, and my sister.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But first-- first my parents were killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then-- and then my sister was still alive but she-- instead of running away from the parents, she was still lying with the parents.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was just hysterical.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[SOBBING] And then the Germans came and took her, and from what we know, I don't know if they shot her or she-- she went.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Exactly I really can't say 100% because I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But from what I heard, that she was shot dead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And this-- this is how I lost my parents and my sister.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was the start.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were in the hiding then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were there for-- for a little while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Germans were very clever because they knew the Jews hiding somewhere.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they declared an amnesty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we-- we were not sure if this is just a trick or something and they will get us and kill us all.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they-- no, the-- what we heard is that everyone can go back to their homes, and everything will be all right.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
